DP William Ruto has assembled a team described as Sky Team members to lead his campaigns. They include MP Aden Duale (Garissa Township) and Senator Kithure Kindiki (Tharaka Nithi), Nyali MP Mohamed Ali and South Mugirango MP Sylvanus Osoro and Kiharu MP Ndindi Nyoro. Others are Alice Wahome, Rigathi Gachagua, Kipchumba Murkomen, Kimani Ichung’wah (Kikuyu) and Kimilili MP Didmas Barasa and Aisha Jumwa. They are expected to lead campaigns in the Central, Rift Valley and Coast regions. The politicians have the charisma and oratorical skills helping to energise Ruto’s campaign messages and confront rivals as campaigns approach the crescendo.